# GRAPHICS::UI3DSCENE_IS_AVAILABLE

## Returns
* **BOOL**

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Returns whether the UI 3D scene manager is not in use already: only one user can interface with the
manager at a given time.
